poker

Class JDECPokerBot

  • java.lang.Object
    • poker.JDECPokerBot

  • public class JDECPokerBot
extends java.lang.Object
    A poker bot which searches for Twitter statuses using the Twitter API, and creates playable GameOfPoker instances.
    Author:
    Dara Callinan, Jazheel Luna, Eoghan O'Donnell, Crischelle Pana

        Class constructor. Initialises the playing list, activeGames array and searchBegin date. Reads Twitter API keys from keys file, and connects to the Twitter API.
